attributes.Long form description: The student starts by rotating the rolling cart to loosen the wheels to unscrew them. Once the wheels are loosened, the student unscrews the wheels and removes them from the rolling cart. The student unscrews the side bolts to remove the brackets of the rolling cart, followed by rotating it to remove the trays and stack them together, At the end of the video, the student dissasembles the side bars and the base frame to end the tasks.
